data.description: Looking for a quiet neighborhood in a convenient location? This 5 bed 3 bath home is located in the Cumberland Point neighborhood in the Highlands. The home features natural light flooding throughout, bed and full bath downstairs perfect for mother in law suite, storage space for all your holiday decorations and more, and screened in patio overlooking serene lagoon. The stunning kitchen boasts all stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, tile backsplash, and pantry with room for all your kitchen essentials. The spacious master suite features an ensuite bathroom with double vanities, separate water closet, garden tub, walk in shower, and his and her closets. Additional features include living room bookcase built ins and fireplace, office, laundry room, loft space, and access to resort style amenities such as pool with water slide, gym, tennis courts, playground, and more. Located moments from everything Pooler has to offer, as well as easy interstate access! 3D tour available.
